      <title>加拿大育空地区寻求将维多利亚黄金公司纳入破产管理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/canada-s-yukon-seeks-to-place-victoria-gold-into-receivership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年夏初，维多利亚黄金公司的旗舰金矿发生严重山体滑坡和氰化物泄漏事故，加拿大某领土的政府正试图将该金矿纳入破产管理程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/canada-s-yukon-seeks-to-place-victoria-gold-into-receivership</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TCW、Saba 认为股市“恐慌指数”反映信贷市场风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/tcw-saba-see-credit-market-risk-in-stocks-fear-gauge-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥利维亚·雷蒙德 (Olivia Raimonde) 在“彭博未平仓合约”节目中表示，包括 TCW 集团和 Boaz Weinstein 的 Saba Capital 在内的信贷投资者看到，VIX 指标对债券市场发出了警告，VIX 指标被称为股市的“恐慌指标”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/tcw-saba-see-credit-market-risk-in-stocks-fear-gauge-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:40:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通凯利呼吁美联储降息 50 个基点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/jpmorgan-s-kelly-calls-for-a-50-bps-fed-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通资产管理公司首席全球策略师戴维·凯利在接受彭博电视采访时表示：“我希望美联储加息 50 个基点，但前提是美联储必须将此作为正常化的一部分。”(来源：彭博社)]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/jpmorgan-s-kelly-calls-for-a-50-bps-fed-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>M&M’S 制造商 Mars 以 360 亿美元收购 Kellanova</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/m-m-s-maker-mars-to-buy-kellanova-for-36-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛氏公司 (Mars Inc.) 是 M&amp;M’S 和士力架等流行零食的制造商，该公司将以约 360 亿美元收购品客薯片制造商 Kellanova。这是今年最大的一笔交易，两家大型食品公司联手。Crystal Tse 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/m-m-s-maker-mars-to-buy-kellanova-for-36-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:35:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度改变电力出口规则，阿达尼或将获益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/india-changes-power-export-rules-in-potential-gain-for-adani</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度对电力生产商出口电力出台了新规定，允许他们在国内市场销售电力。此举可能使阿达尼电力有限公司的电厂受益，该电厂向孟加拉国出口电力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/india-changes-power-export-rules-in-potential-gain-for-adani</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 14:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀回落，债券交易员预计下个月降息四分之一个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/bond-traders-trim-bets-on-fed-rate-cuts-after-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国通胀持续回落，债券投资者加强押注美联储官员将在九月份将利率降低四分之一个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/bond-traders-trim-bets-on-fed-rate-cuts-after-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 13:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团的德怀特·斯科特在打造信贷巨头后将退休</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/blackstone-s-scott-to-retire-after-building-credit-colossus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的内部备忘录显示，德怀特·斯科特 (Dwight Scott) 即将退休，他曾帮助黑石集团的信贷业务发展成为价值 3,300 亿美元的庞然大物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/blackstone-s-scott-to-retire-after-building-credit-colossus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 13:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
